programme.desc: Elizabeth Welsh's husband, Patrick, left her and their two sons what appeared to be a suicide note and disappeared. After investigating the situation, Elizabeth discovered that Patrick is still alive, living in Texas.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Getting Away with Murder?
programme.desc: A report on families who have experienced the violent death of a loved one and believe they know the identity of the killer but lack evidence to back the charge.

programme.title: 48 Hours: A Mother Accused
programme.desc: This report investigates alleged incidents of Shaken Baby Syndrome, focusing on accusations involving Paulette and Kelly Welch, a Mormon couple living in Idaho Falls, Idaho, whose adopted son Stockton died on May 1, 1999 following a fall in their home.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Murder in Spokane
programme.desc: A report that focuses on the murders in Spokane, Washington over a period of a little more than two years (1997 - 1999) of at least a dozen women, mostly prostitutes.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Murder They Wrote: The End of the Dream
programme.desc: A report on the charismatic Scott Scurlock, known as “Hollywood” because of his flamboyant style and effective use of disguises in the commission of crimes, successfully eluded capture for four years while effortlessly robbing 18 banks.
programme.sub-title: Murder They Wrote: The End of the Dream

programme.title: 48 Hours: A Cop Behind Bars
programme.desc: Patrick Bradford, was convicted of stabbing his mistress to death. Determined to win his acquittal, Deborah Nolan, a close friend, and staunch supporter of Bradford’s, quit her teaching job and went to law school to take on his defense.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Murder in Las Vegas
programme.desc: Ron Rudin, a wealthy real-estate developer disappeared from his home in Las Vegas, Nev. Later, the charred remains of his decapitated body were found in the desert. After a lengthy investigation police were convinced that Rudin’s wife was involved.

programme.title: 48 Hours: A Family Torn Apart
programme.desc: The murdered body of Bob Dorotik, a engineer and father of three, was found by a mountain road near his home in the foothills of San Diego, Ca. Despite her denial of any involvement, Jane, Dorotik’s wife of 30 years, was arrested for the crime.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Double Jeopardy
programme.desc: The investigation of the September 24, 1988 sexual torture-murder in Louisville, Kentucky, of Brenda Sue Schaefer.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Fatal Attraction
programme.desc: Thomas Capano, a successful Delaware lawyer lived a double life, a devoted family man while having affairs. When Anne Marie Fahey, one of these women, mysteriously disappeared police were at first stumped. Finally evidence led to Capano.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Bitter Pill
programme.desc: Stella Nickell of Auburn, Washington, was sentenced to 90 year in federal prison for poisoning her husband Bruce and Sue Snow, a Seattle bank manager with cyanide-laced Excedrin.

programme.title: 48 Hours: The Mystery of Slide Mountain
programme.desc: A report that examines evidence and unanswered questions regarding a June 1, 1998 auto accident on Slide Mountain, near Reno, Nevada, that led to the death of Rinette Riella Bergna and left the driver, Rinette’s husband Peter with only minor injuries.

programme.title: 48 Hours: The Colonel's Wife
programme.desc: Ret. Col. George Maracek, a 69-year-old former Green Beret who served in Korea and Vietnam, has been charged with the 1991 murder of his Thai wife Viparet. He maintains that he is innocent.

programme.title: 48 Hours: Reasonable Doubt
programme.desc: In September 1999, Brian Eftenoff of Phoenix, Az. Was convicted of murdering his wife, Judi. It was alleged that Eftenoff forced more than a gram of cocaine down his wife’s throat causing her to die of a cocaine-induced stroke.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2316
programme.desc: En ny resa väntar Catherine Southon och Serhat Ahmet när de beger sig från Kent till London på jakt efter antika skatter som är både unika och värdefulla.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2317
programme.desc: Serhat Ahmet och Catherine Southon ger sig ut på en ny resa med antikviteter i East Midlands och letar efter gömda skatter i lokala butiker.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2318
programme.desc: Serhat Ahmet och Catherine Southon kör längs East Anglias kust i sin klassiska bil på jakt efter prisvärda antikviteter och regionala skatter.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2319
programme.desc: Antikvarieexperterna Catherine Southon och Serhat Ahmet har en stram budget för sin sista shoppingresa. De måste vara smarta med sina pengar för att göra en vinst på den kommande auktionen.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2320
programme.desc: Catherine Southon och Serhat Ahmet står inför sin sista chans att göra stora investeringar. Frågan kvarstår, vem kommer att vinna och ta hem segern på auktionen?

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2321
programme.desc: Margie Cooper och Paul Martin reser genom Somerset på jakt efter värdefulla föremål. Margie siktar på Edwardianska möbler och stamkonst, medan Paul hoppas på en stor avkastning på sina investeringar.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2322
programme.desc: Margie Cooper och Paul Martin ger sig ut i Somerset på jakt efter lukrativa antikviteter. Margie gör ett klokt val med en leksak i oskadat skick, medan Paul tar en risk med en viktoriansk toalett.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2323
programme.desc: Margie Cooper och Paul Martin reser västerut på jakt efter värdefulla antikviteter. Paul förvärvar ett viktigt piratföremål, medan Margie visar intresse för skimrande silverföremål.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2324
programme.desc: Paul Martin och Margie Cooper reser genom Cornwall på jakt efter värdefulla antikviteter. Paul köper en mjölkpall från förr i tiden, medan Margie väljer ett högljutt bilhorn från 1920-talet.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2325
programme.desc: Margie Cooper och Paul Martin har kommit till Plymouth. Ett varierat urval av antikviteter kommer att skapa en fängslande auktion, men vilken expert kommer att krönas till den ultimata antikjägaren?

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2401
programme.desc: Experterna Natasha Raskin Sharp och James Braxton tävlar om att hitta de mest lönsamma antikviteterna när de reser genom Devon i en Porsche från 1970-talet. Det slutar med koskällor och ett intresse för åsnemjölk.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2402
programme.desc: Natasha och James köper elefanter efter att ha letat runt bland antikvariaten i Devon och Somerset, men resan tar en farlig vändning när Braxton hamnar på en racerbana i en gammal bil.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2403
programme.desc: I Somerset och Wiltshire upptäcker Natasha en kärlek till stolar, medan James köper föremål i perfekt skick när de utforskar antikvariat.

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2404
programme.desc: När Natasha utforskar Wiltshire upptäcker hon ett holländskt mästerverk och köpslår hårt för det, medan James sätter sitt hopp till en stygg hund. Kommer deras vinster att räcka till?

programme.title: Antiques Road Trip: Avsnitt 2405
programme.desc: I Oxfordshire utforskar James skjul fyllda med antikviteter medan Natasha upptäcker konst. Vem kommer att vinna?

programme.title: Dr. Phil: The Fight Over A Little Boy: Who's Tellng The Truth? Pt. 1
programme.desc: Megan's ex-boyfriend Andy is trying to replace her as their 5-year-old son's mother with his new fiancée, Caitlin. Megan says Andy lied to the judge, falsely painting her as unfit, unstable & a drug addict. Andy says Megan's tale of woe is a sob story.
programme.sub-title: The Fight Over A Little Boy: Who's Tellng The Truth? Pt. 1

programme.title: Dr. Phil: The Mystery Of Melissa: Why Did She Vanish? Pt. 1
programme.desc: Melissa, 26, left home without warning & flew 2,000 miles across the country, leaving behind a note that said, "One day, Dr. Phil will be able to help me." The family says she hadn't "been herself." Melissa says she's ready to tell why she vanished.
programme.sub-title: The Mystery Of Melissa: Why Did She Vanish? Pt. 1

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Our Daughter Is Raising Our Grandson In A Filthy Death Trap
programme.desc: Fred & Cynthia say daughter, Crystal, is raising her young son in a death trap! No running water, leaky ceiling, exposed wires, smoking electrical sockets, mice & mold! They are ready for CPS. Crystal says her home is a visible form of how she feels.
programme.sub-title: Our Daughter Is Raising Our Grandson In A Filthy Death Trap

programme.title: Dr. Phil: From Tech-Genius To Unmotivated Mess
programme.desc: Logan, 30, desperately needs help. Mom Tracy says he has gone from a productive computer science engineer to a shell of a human being: no motivation, rarely eats, & can barely function to take care of his basic hygiene needs. Can Logan get back on track?

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Help! My Handicapped Husband Treats Me Like A Slave
programme.desc: Natalie's husband, Brian, was in a tragic work accident, falling from a 68-foot crane. Paralyzed from the knees down, she says Brian treats her & son Jacob, 13, like slaves not family. Their marriage has changed; Brian says it's too painful to even move.
programme.sub-title: Help! My Handicapped Husband Treats Me Like A Slave

programme.title: Dr. Phil: My Dad Believes He's Married To A Woman Named "Maria" He's Never Met Pt. 1
programme.desc: Shelby wants to find the truth about her dad's online relationship with a woman he's never met. Dad David says "Maria" has a $10 million inheritance and says he knows for a fact that "Maria" is a real person and he can't wait to introduce her one day.
programme.sub-title: My Dad Believes He's Married To A Woman Named "Maria" He's Never Met Pt. 1

programme.title: Dr. Phil: An Abusive Father Or A Delusional Teen: Who Is Telling The Truth? Pt. 2
programme.desc: Tensions run high in this father/daughter battle conclusion. McKinley, 18, confronts her dad for allegedly being "abusive" in her childhood & a "pedophile," claims he denies. Dr. Phil questions Cory on an incident leading to Cory's sexual battery arrest.
programme.sub-title: An Abusive Father Or A Delusional Teen: Who Is Telling The Truth? Pt. 2

programme.title: Dr. Phil: A Father Accused, A Mother Blamed, The Truth Revealed Pt. 2
programme.desc: Dr. Phil continues with Megan, her ex-boyfriend, Andy and his fiancee Caitlin, who have presented Dr. Phil with evidence supporting their allegation that it is Megan's own lifestyle & choices keeping her out of her son's life. Who is telling the truth?
programme.sub-title: A Father Accused, A Mother Blamed, The Truth Revealed Pt. 2

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Is "Maria" Real? A Big Surprise For David Pt. 2
programme.desc: David says he's in love with "Maria", a Christian woman from Texas with a $10 million inheritance. Even though they've never met, he's paid $25,000 to their lawyer to assist her in receiving her inheritance. Dr. Phil investigates "Maria": real or catfish?
programme.sub-title: Is "Maria" Real? A Big Surprise For David Pt. 2

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Do Words Matter Or Are We Too Sensitive?
programme.desc: People, eager to give opinions, can lose an entire career with just one tweet. Kathy won Miss Michigan 2019 but lost the crown the next day because of comments she made on social media.Plus, Carissa's transphobic posts derailed her dreams.
programme.sub-title: Do Words Matter Or Are We Too Sensitive?

programme.title: Dr. Phil: The Disappearance Of Jennifer Dulos
programme.desc: The disappearance of Connecticut mom of 5, Jennifer Dulos has captivated the media. Dr. Phil's team of experts analyze circumstances surrounding her disappearance, including Jennifer Dulos' estranged husband, Fotis, & his girlfriend, Michelle Troconis.

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Our 15-Year-Old Runaway Daughter Claims She’s Pregnant, but Is She, Part 1
programme.desc: Maribeth and John say their 15-year-old daughter, Marie, has become distant, angry, and is no longer a charming honors student. Marie acts out, her parents place restrictions, and Marie runs away. Upon returning, Marie now claims she's pregnant. Part 1
programme.sub-title: Our 15-Year-Old Runaway Daughter Claims She’s Pregnant, but Is She, Part 1

programme.title: Dr. Phil: My Ex-husband Blew Our Million Dollar Retirement, Part 1
programme.desc: Robert, a retired professor, says he began dating as his 40-year marriage unraveled. Wife Jeremi says Robert spent their $1 million savings on day trading and giving money to women, who she insists are catfish. Dr. Phil finds out what is going on. Part 1
programme.sub-title: My Ex-husband Blew Our Million Dollar Retirement, Part 1

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Terrorized By My 10-Year-Old
programme.desc: Alisha says her son, Kevin, 10, pushed the family to the limit with violent outbursts. At home, knives and lighters are hidden & siblings lock themselves in their rooms at night. Alisha's says the 'future Kevin' may hurt the entire family or end a life.

programme.title: Dr. Phil: My Boyfriend Is Married & His Wife Is Irrelvant To Me
programme.desc: Brooklyn, 18, says she is tired of her mom butting into her love life with boyfriend Eric. Mom Courtney says it's because Brooklyn's boyfriend has two children & a wife! Eric's wife, Mandy, wants Brooklyn to leave her husband alone & she'll fight for him.
programme.sub-title: My Boyfriend Is Married & His Wife Is Irrelvant To Me

programme.title: Dr. Phil: Help! I’m Going to Inherit a Messy Mansion, Millions and My Adult Sister
programme.desc: Lydia says she's living in her dream home with a view reminding her of Italy and of being in love. Daughter Kim calls it an overcrowded and messy mansion and is afraid she'll inherit the mess, plus her sister who lives in the basement! Dr. Phil mediates!
programme.sub-title: Help! I’m Going to Inherit a Messy Mansion, Millions and My Adult Sister

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 113
programme.desc: En miljöinspektör är på väg in och kommer att dela ut en stor makt till någon i huset. Nu gäller det att verkligen göra ett bra första intryck för att kunna styra vem som får vara kvar i huset!

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 114
programme.desc: Kvällen innan handlar om kärlek och hångel, men morgonen efter handlar om miljöförstörelse, miljöbovar och tuffa val. Nicholas får en möjlighet att ge tillbaka gentjänsten han tidigare fått av nya Jonathan.

programme.title: Paradise
programme.desc: Mathilda och Agnes startar en hemlig pakt. Det har även blivit dags för ett nytt eldigt Pandoras box. Det kommer in brev om en stundande klimatkris som sätter allt på sin spets.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 116
programme.desc: Linnea och Jonathan hänger löst inför kvällens partnerceremoni, och Agnes har en möjlighet att skicka ut en väldigt stark spelare. Men tar hon sin chans så finns det stor risk att hon får gruppen emot sig.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 117
programme.desc: Det har blivit dags för Paradise Prisvecka! Nu finns det både en hemlig tjejpakt och en hemlig järnhandspakt i huset. En kung och en drottning är på väg för att dela ut priser och röra om i spelet.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 118
programme.desc: Ett poesipris ska delas ut! Och hur kommer det gå för den hemliga tjejpakten nu när Agnes bästa kompisar har kommit tillbaka till huset? Kommer de andra tjejerna kunna lita på henne?

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 119
programme.desc: Det har blivit dags för fysikprov. Ett prov baserat bara på kunskap, vilket gör pakterna osäkra. Nu kan ju vem som helst vinna. Det ska även delas ut ett fredspris som för med sig ett väldigt tufft beslut!

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 120
programme.desc: Eddy har ett tufft val som fredspristagare framför sig då han måste skicka hem kung Andreas eller drottning Mellami! Jasmine hänger löst vilket tvingar järnhandspakten till att börja agera i det öppna.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 121
programme.desc: En känd influencer är på väg till huset i rollen som häxjägare för att anklaga och avslöja häxorna i huset. Pedro litar inte längre på järnhandspakten efter att de tidigare inte lyckades rädda Jasmine.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 122
programme.desc: Agnes, Matilda, Isak och Jonte har blivit häxor och hänger löst inför en stundande partnerceremoni. Under pandoras ask grillas Matilda hårt om vilka hon egentligen spelar med.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 123
programme.desc: Linnea och Isak ryker ihop under pandoras ask och Nicci får chansen att skona en häxa hon litar på. En domare är på väg till huset för att förhöra alla häxor och Isak blir väldigt nervös.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 101
programme.desc: 11 förväntansfulla deltagare flyttar in till paradiset i Mexiko. Det är dags för deltagarna att lära känna varandra, och snabbt lista ut vem man kan lita på och inte.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 102
programme.desc: Det har blivit dags för årets första fest i Paradise. Vissa tar sig friheter, och missnöjet bubblar i huset. Ett brev kommer in och kastar om allt i huset. Ingen är längre säker på sin plats.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 103
programme.desc: Det har blivit dags att välja. Kan de gående lita på sina nya partners eller behöver de ta över deras säkra stolsplatser för att få vara kvar i paradiset? Partnerceremonin börjar närma sig...

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 104
programme.desc: Efter att Pedro blivit immun så hänger nu Yang löst och riskerar att behöva lämna paradiset. Aissa tvingas till att ta ett riktigt tufft beslut. Ska hon hålla sitt löfte eller följa sitt hjärta?

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 105
programme.desc: Ny vecka I paradiset med astrologi-tema. En astrolog är på väg in och kommer få mycket makt över gruppen inför partnerceremonin. Allt drama gör att Isak blir väldigt osäker på om han kan lita på Aissa.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 106
programme.desc: Astrologen Mathilda har ett tufft beslut framför sig. Hon ska utse en ormbärare. Vad det betyder vet ingen, vilket gör deltagarna väldigt nervösa.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 107
programme.desc: Spåmannen Sebastian har dolt två kulor under skynken. Hittar ormbäraren Isak den gröna kulan så får han stanna i Paradiset och blir immun, men om han hittar den röda kulan så måste han omedelbart lämna.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 108
programme.desc: Det har blivit dags för partnerceremoni. Mellami hänger löst, vilket kräver drastiska beslut från hennes hemliga pakt med Andreas och Agnes. Beslut som gör att de andra deltagarna känner sig väldigt svikna.

programme.title: Paradise: Avsnitt 109
programme.desc: Deltagarna vaknar upp till kärlekstema i paradiset. Det har bildats många nya par i huset. Men kan deltagarna lita på sina nya partners? Det smids hemliga planer för att skapa nya par.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Falkenberg
programme.desc: Something is definitely happening in Falkenberg on the west coast of Sweden. Over the last couple of years it have become somewhat of a haven for foodies. Tareq is on a mission; taking him through a fertile landscape with vineyards and salmon fishing.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Estonia (Part 2)
programme.desc: Estonia has embarked on a journey greatly inspired by the nordic cuisine. Tareq explores the countryside of Estonia before he returns to the capital of Tallinn where he meets people that really love their traditional food.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Öland
programme.desc: Tareq bikes through the unique landscape of Öland, Sweden's second largest island located in the Baltic Sea. It is a place where the interaction between man and nature have created a diverse and rich farmland with an amazing amount of small producers.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Bornholm
programme.desc: Bornholm, the sunny bright green island with it’s own gastronomic tone is a true pioneer when it comes to local food at it’s finest quality. Tareq visit Denmark's first regional food culture house where they develop this unique flourishing cuisine.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Laponia
programme.desc: In the northern part of Sweden, you’ll find the stunning world heritage Laponia. Almost 10.000 square kilometres of nature reserves and national parks. Tareq visit the rich, unique culture of the sami in the vast impressive wilderness.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Malmö & Copenhagen
programme.desc: Tareq Taylor returns to his home turf to see what has happened and what the future might bring to the new nordic cuisine. He visits a local goat farmer and meets up with young enthusiastic chefs who takes this nordic legacy further.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Zealand
programme.desc: Tareq Taylor visits the South Coast of Denmark to make his own versions of open-faced sandwiches and smoked fish dishes.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Dalsland
programme.desc: Tareq Taylor puts on his hiking boots and explores the pilgrim trail of Dalsland in West Sweden. This episode will include outdoor cooking, foraging and beaver safari.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Stockholm
programme.desc: When Tareq arrives in Stockholm he will meet innovation and world class gastronomy, a big city for foodies. He will make some pizza at the Rosendal garden café and go on an adventure in the archipielago.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Lolland
programme.desc: When Michelin star chefs move from Copenhagen to the countryside, they often end up in Lolland/Falster. Here Tareq will meet Claus Meyer the father of new nordic cuisine and other entrepreneurs that opened interesting restaurants here.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Skåne
programme.desc: Tareq Taylor explores his own backyard of Skåne and hometown of Malmö, a multi cultural food mix. Here you can find food and culture from all over the world that makes it a unique culinary destination.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Best Of
programme.desc: Tareq Taylor looks back on some of the food adventures he has been part of in the program series Nordic Cookery. Tareq promises delicacies from all over the Nordics and meetings with fantastic people along the way.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Läckö & Kinnekulle
programme.desc: By Lake Vänern you find Läckö and Kinnekulle, an area rich in history, culture and traditions. Tareq cooks exciting dishes on vendice roe, fish and local cheeses - all served on porcelain from the world-famous Rörstrand.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Sjuhärad
programme.desc: Sjuhärad is nature and culture in perfect symbiosis. Tareq takes the bike to meet some of the food entrepreneurs in the area who have started exciting new businesses. Here you live close to nature, forest and lakes.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Greater Copenhagen
programme.desc: Copenhagen and Skåne are a hot food destinations. Tareq visits Østergro, Denmark's first "rooftop farm" in the middle of Copenhagen, Eden in the new district Hyllie, Malmö and Häckeberga Castle where there will be wild boar for dinner.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Höganäs
programme.desc: The wild coast at Kullaberg in Skåne has a lot of culture and gastronomy to offer. Fantastic ceramics, vineyards and world-class ice cream. Tareq visits VikenTomater and cooks vegetarian ragù

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Karlstad
programme.desc: Tareq visits sunny Karlstad! Here, food is prepared by Vänern's shores and in Värmland's deep forests. Butter-fried Zander, crepes and cooking over an open fire are on the menu.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Best Of (Part 2)
programme.desc: Once again, Tareq Taylor looks back on some of the food adventures he has been part of in the program series Nordic Cookery. Tareq promises delicacies from all over the Nordics and meetings with fantastic people along the way.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Lund
programme.desc: In this episode, Tareq visits Lund, a thousand-year old city in southern Sweden. Lund is surrounded by the richest farmland in the country, and we explore nearby islands and meet entrepreneurs making highly-regarded local products.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Bornholm
programme.desc: Tareq sails out to Bornholm, a Danish island close to southern tip of Sweden. The islanders are fiercely self-sufficient and this attitude reflects in the huge number of food producers making products that are sold both locally and internationally.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Jokkmokk
programme.desc: Far above the Arctic Circle, Tareq explores the wild country around Jokkmokk. Here, the Sami people lived from what the land provides for thousands of years. This wild cuisine is as extreme as the weather here.

programme.title: Tareq Taylor's Nordic Cookery: Åland
programme.desc: For hundreds of years, Åland’s shipping fleet was the envy of navies around the world, and their sea trade was encouraged by the seafood, grains and fruits that thrive on these islands. Tareq prepares recipes to reflect Åland’s unique cuisine.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Adeline Piet Case

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Shot At Point-Blank: The Aurelie Barbot Affair

programme.sub-title: Shot At Point-Blank: The Aurelie Barbot Affair

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: A Night of Horror at Devil's Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case)
programme.desc: On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed.
programme.sub-title: A Night of Horror at Devil's Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case)

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Evelyne Boucher Case
programme.desc: On December 9th 1987, the naked body of the young Evelyne Boucher is found near Avignon. An unprecedented investigation begins making headlines.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Two Accused of Murder (Jennifer Charron Case)
programme.desc: On Sunday, April 29, 2007, the body of Jennifer Charron, 21-years old, was found burnt to a crisp in a forest near Royan. The young waitress, who had been missing for two days, was visibly beaten and tied up.
programme.sub-title: Two Accused of Murder (Jennifer Charron Case)

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Nelly Crémel Case
programme.desc: Nelly Crémel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. There's no doubt that it's murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell Case
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains. Taken to hospital, the couple die several days apart. The food poisoning theory is quickly ruled out and forensic tests show the Labrells were poisoned with arsenic.
programme.sub-title: The Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell Case

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Mystery of Room 602 (Ve´ronique Pirotton Case)
programme.desc: On October 31, 2013, Belgian politician Bernard Ouessfal rushed down the six flights of a hotel in Ostend where he had met up with his wife, Véronique, the day before. He had found her unconscious in the bathroom with a mysterious plastic bag next to her
programme.sub-title: The Mystery of Room 602 (Ve´ronique Pirotton Case)

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Savage Murder of a Mother and her Daughter (Amato Case)
programme.desc: On March 31, 2003, firefighters were called to a fire in a housing estate of Meyrargues, near Aix-en-Provence. On site, they discovered a horrific scene: the tortured and charred bodies of a mother and her daughter, Chantal and Audrey D'Amato.
programme.sub-title: The Savage Murder of a Mother and her Daughter (Amato Case)

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Josiane Bézard Case

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: Two Young Women Massacred: The Leconte Affair

programme.sub-title: Two Young Women Massacred: The Leconte Affair

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers: The Priscillia Ciatti Case

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Village of Vengeance: Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Village of Vengeance: Part 2
programme.desc: It's the showdown in the sands between the bandit Bakura and his ever-growing Diabound versus the Pharaoh, Mahad the Dark Magician, and the remaining guardians of the Pharaoh!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Village of Vengeance: Part 3
programme.desc: With the help of his father's spirit, the Pharaoh and his guardians defeated the bandit Bakura's Diabound and stopped the horrible Zorc from resurrecting... or did they?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Village of Vengeance: Part 4
programme.desc: The Pharaoh's journey was more than a trip to the past, it's the greatest Shadow Game ever created. Yami Yugi and Yami Bakura's Shadow Game has already reached apocalyptic proportions, but it's only the beginning of cataclysmic events!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Village of Vengeance: Part 5
programme.desc: Zorc's incredible shadow energies have resurrected the bandit Bakura and his Diabound. With a second chance at revenge, the bandit king has broken up the Pharaoh's team so that he can divide and conquer them one at a time!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: Name of the Game
programme.desc: The hope of mankind rests on Yugi's shoulders as he arrives at the final temple chamber where the Pharaoh's name is located, but something unexpected is waiting for them - a sinister surprise that can cost them their lives!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Dark One Cometh: Part 1
programme.desc: After a nearly eternal slumber, the all-powerful Zorc has resurrected, plunging the world into darkness!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Dark One Cometh: Part 2
programme.desc: The Pharaoh and his guardians are down to their last line of defense as Shada falls victim to Zorc. The Pharaoh desperately wants to summon the three Egyptian Gods, but he can't without his Millennium Puzzle!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Dark One Cometh: Part 3
programme.desc: Exodia the Forbidden One couldn't defeat Zorc! Exodia was able to buy enough time for the Pharaoh to get his Millennium Puzzle back-he can now summon the almighty Egyptian Gods! It's time for the Pharaoh's counterattack in the biggest brawl.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Dark One Cometh: Part 4
programme.desc: The three Egyptian Gods have been defeated. The Pharaoh is severely hurt and unable to stop Zorc from setting fire to the city, but our heroes aren't giving up. It's not double vision when Seto and Kaiba transcend time to confront Zorc.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: In the Name of the Pharaoh
programme.desc: The Pharaoh and Kaiba's combined strength couldn't defeat Zorc. Yugi must give the Pharaoh his name, but Yugi doesn't know how to read ancient Egyptian text. All bets are off in the final clash where Yugi must protect the past to save the future!
programme.sub-title: In the Name of the Pharaoh

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Final Journey
programme.desc: Pharaoh Atem, Yugi, and friends have defeated the bandit Bakura and Zorc, but the final test still awaits! Yugi must duel Atem! As they set sail to the final dueling grounds, everyone realizes this may be the final night Yugi and Atem have together.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Final Duel: Part 1
programme.desc: If Yugi defeats Atem, Yugi will prove he's ready to stand on his own, and Atem can join his friends in the world beyond. But Yugi and Atem will be separated forever.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Final Duel: Part 2
programme.desc: Atem has summoned all three Egyptian Gods! What chance does Yugi have against these powerful creatures that no one has been able to defeat? Yugi better think of a strategy quickly or this duel will be over soon!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Final Duel: Part 3
programme.desc: Atem still has all three Egyptian God Cards, Yugi doesn't have a single monster on the field! Yugi claims that he has a combo that will defeat the Egyptian Gods, but is he simply bragging, or does he actually have a plan?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh!: The Final Duel: Part 4
programme.desc: Yugi and Atem - more than friends, closer than brothers. Will they stay together, or is it time to say goodbye? It's the final answer, the final duel, and the final time we will see our friends in the rousing conclusion to Yu-Gi-Oh!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! The Movie
programme.desc: Heroic Yugi squares off against archrival Kaiba in an adventure even more dangerous when the imaginary monsters in their playing cards become ferociously real…and when an old evil enters the fray.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The Next King of Games
programme.desc: When Jaden arrives late to his entrance exam for Duel Academy, he has to go above and beyond expectations to prove that he deserves to make the cut.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Welcome to Duel Academy
programme.desc: The incoming class is welcomed to Duel Academy, but Jaden finds a less-than-warm reception from freshman hotshot Chazz when he's challenged to a duel.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: A Duel in Love
programme.desc: When Syrus stumbles into the girls' dorm, he puts himself and Jaden in danger of being expelled, forcing Jaden to win a duel to win their freedom.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX
programme.desc: On test day at Duel Academy, Dr. Crowler steals a new card shipment to stack the deck against Jaden and embarrass him in front of the entire school!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The Shadow Duelist, Part 1
programme.desc: When Jaden and the crew wander into an abandoned dorm, they encounter a mysterious duelist who claims he's taken Alexis to the Shadow Realm, and unless Jaden duels him, he's going to keep her there.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: The Shadow Duelist, Part 2
programme.desc: Jaden continues his duel with the mysterious Shadow Duelist, fighting now not just for Alexis' soul, but for his own.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Duel and Unusual Punishment
programme.desc: Having been caught for trespassing into the abandoned dorm, Jaden and Syrus are sentenced to a tag team duel. If they lose, they'll be expelled.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: For the Sake of Syrus
programme.desc: To help Syrus overcome some serious confidence issues, Jaden looks to duel Zane, Syrus' older brother, and the best duelist at Duel Academy.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Family Business
programme.desc: When Chumley's father comes to remove him from Duel Academy, Jaden and Syrus stand by their friend when he tries to outduel his father so he can stay.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! GX: Tag Team Trial, Part 1
programme.desc: The tag match to determine Jaden and Syrus's fate at Duel Academy begins, but not just against any tag team: against the legendary Paradox Brothers!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Serious Send Off!
programme.desc: Det är sista hela dagen i huset och gänget förbereder sig för att fira det, Nathan låter Bethan 'rumpvaxa' honom, Nat lagar avskedsmiddag och Chloe hänger med ut sista kvällen på stan - det kommer bli kanon!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Get This Party Started!
programme.desc: Gänget ser fram emot inflytten, och de flesta är singel. De får träffa två nykomlingar, Amelia och Ant, och visar dem hur man festar. Allt är bara fint tills Nathan och Beau kommer varandra nära, för nära enligt Bethan.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Family Friction!
programme.desc: Gänget lär känna nykomlingarna. Det kommer en överraskning när Anna beordrar dem att be om ursäkt å en festprisses vägnar. Allt brakar loss när Chloe ignorerar Nathans råd att inte komma Ant för nära.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: It's Fright Night!
programme.desc: Chloes känslor för Ant börjar avta, men han är hoppfull efter att ha fått sova i hennes säng. Gänget blir vettskrämda efter en skogspromenad, och Abbie och Chloe tvingas snacka ut för första gången på länge.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Hello New Lad!
programme.desc: Nykomlingen Louis lämnar avtryck direkt. Chloe faller för hans charm till Ants förtret. Gänget har en vild hemmafest där Ant konfronterar Chloe, och Bethan säger till Beau att hon behöver mer uppmärksamhet.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Big Mistake!
programme.desc: Louis kritiserar Chloe för hennes ursäkt til Ant, så hon hånglar med Ant. Beau och Bethan snackar ut och kommer överens, men sen blir Beau full och gör bort sig.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: See Ya, Nat!
programme.desc: Nat har inte mått bra och bestämmer sig för att ta bort tatueringen med exets namn för att må bättre. Men efter att ha funderat bestämmer hon sig för att åka för gott. Beau och Bethan har ett spänt samtal om framtiden.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Chloe Changes Her Ways!
programme.desc: Bethan bestämmer sig för att åka hem för att jobba med sig själv men Beau stannar kvar. På en fest i huset gör Ant att Louis och Chloe blir osams, vilket orsakar osämja bland killarna. Chloe visar äntligen att hon är en stark, oberoende kvinna!

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Geordie-licious!
programme.desc: Det är sista kvällen och gänget ska vara värdar för ett evenemang som heter Geordie-licious! De känner pressen att fixa en fest som alla kommer att minnas. Amelia sjunger och killarna strippar. Louis och Chloe verkar vilja samma sak.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: The Singles Have Landed
programme.desc: Efter en allt för lång karantän är Geordiegänget tillbaka! Men den här gången delar de huset med ett gäng sexiga singlar de ska dejta.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Someone's Getting Dumped
programme.desc: Amelia återvänder till huset, James och Louis slåss om Roxy, och singlarna får chockerande nyheter.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Chloe Shoots Her Shot
programme.desc: Abbie hamnar mitt i ett storbråk, Nathan blir rånad, och Chloe lägger in en stöt på Louis.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Return Of The Mac
programme.desc: Nathan konfronterar Nathaniel, James sitter fast i en skotsk macka, och en chockerande återkomst hotar Chloes och Louis spirande romans.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Kiss Louis Goodbye
programme.desc: Louis satsar allt, men Chloe börjar tveka. Marty kommer att få återuppleva sitt förflutna, och en chockerande vräkning splittrar huset.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Just a Kiss?
programme.desc: Ant har dåliga nyheter till Louis. Chloe går på dejt med en modell, och huset ställs inför den hittills jobbigaste dumpningen.

programme.title: Geordie Shore: Unfinished Business
programme.desc: Marty och Chloe går på dejt, Louis kan inte hålla tyst, och strax före den stora utekvällen kommer ett chockerande besked.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The Blessification
programme.desc: Situation känner sig pånyttfödd efter sin välsignelse, Angelina känner sig vilsen efter mötet med djurmediumet och kamraterna förbereder nästa familjesemester.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The Not-So-International Vacation
programme.desc: Gänget åker på familjesemester och Mike får sig en geografiläxa. Jenni får en stor överraskning och konflikter uppstår på oväntat håll.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Deena's Revenge
programme.desc: Pauly D lär sig spela bingo, Angelina får ett utbrott över sitt försenade bagage, Mike inleder en utredning, och en oroväckande upptäckt chockar gänget.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Happy Birthday, Vinny!
programme.desc: Det hettar till när gänget inser att Deena har prankat dem. Snooki kommer precis i tid för en flytande tikibar och Mikes frihetsfest.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Best Party Planner Ever
programme.desc: A tropical storm rages; Snooki and Angelina re-enact their famous fight; and the roomies party on a boat that's also a mansion. Oh, and did we mention the sex therapist?

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The S**pert
programme.desc: Känslorna svallar när en sexterapeut gräver djupt i Angelinas och Chris förhållande. Sen blir det stökigt när köttbullarna improviserar fram en talkshow. Och ännu stökigare när Mike hittar en lapp från Pauly D.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: The Lie Detector Test
programme.desc: Mike, Snooki, Pauly och Deena samlas för att snacka om Seaside Heights och Vinnys hemlängtan. Och när de tar upp bråket mellan Mike och Snooki blir det lite explosivt.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Livin' La Vida Loca
programme.desc: Mike inser att blondiner har roligare, Pauly tar över Madison Square Garden och det blir full fart på gruppchatten när Angelina är i Mexiko med en man som inte är hennes make.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Spill the Tea
programme.desc: Angelina berättar sin version av historien, Jenni och Nicole försöker att muta Deena för att få höra skvallret medan Pauly planerar en gammal hederlig OG-semester. Samtidigt får Mike och Lauren fatta ett svårt beslut angående Mosey.

programme.title: Jersey Shore Family Vacation: Old Mike vs. New Mike
programme.desc: Vägen till El Paso får en oväntad vändning när Mike får ta emot en massa rykten och anklagelser. Han skickar dem omedelbart till gruppchatten och ett rent helvete bryter ut.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Gone, Baby, Gone
programme.desc: Mike återförenas med sin kanadensiska babe, vilket underhåller hela huset. Angelina berättar vad hon verkligen tycker om sina rumskamrater vilket får Snooki att bli galen och allt går åt fanders.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Girls Like That
programme.desc: Vinny väljer mellan två tjejtyper. Med Angelina ute ur bilden tycker Snooki att det är dags att hon och Jenni blir vänner med Sam. Men Snookis lycka är kortlivad då Mike blir alltmer aggressiv mot henne.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Deja Vu All Over Again
programme.desc: Alla är frustrerade över Mikes beteende. Han får alla utkastade från en klubb, får bilen bortbogserad, bränner nästan ner huset och misslyckas som Paulys ragghjälp. Två gånger!

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Back into the Fold
programme.desc: Pauly och Vin går på en sista dejt med sina Miamitjejer medan Sam och Rons sista måltid utvecklas till ett gräl. Jenni ser till att det blir ordentligt med dramatik i bubbelpoolen med Pauly och Mike.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: Back to the Shore
programme.desc: Vännerna är tillbaka för ännu en galen sommar på Jersey Shore! Eftersom Angelina försvunnit har Snooki tagit med sig sin vän Deena. Spänningen mellan tjejerna från Miami exploderar och snart flyger knytnävar och löshår i luften.

programme.title: Jersey Shore: It's Gonna Be an Interesting Summer
programme.desc: Bråket mellan Sammi och JWoww orsakar spänning i huset. Ronnie och Sammi fortsätter att isolera sig och missar första familjemiddagen. När Ronnie bestämmer sig för att umgås och ha kul med resten av huset känner sig Sammi ensam.
programme.sub-title: It's Gonna Be an Interesting Summer

programme.title: Zoey 101: Hemliga klubben
programme.desc: Logan vill bli medlem i skolans hemliga klubb. Samtidigt insisterar Quinn på att hon aldrig tidigare träffat den nya eleven som just börjat på PCA.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Skolans förbannelse 1
programme.desc: Zoey och gänget undersöker en gammal legend om en PCA-elev som blev galen efter att ha pluggat för mycket inför ett svårt prov. Efter att de råkat störa studentens grav börjar han hemsöka skolan.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Skolans förbannelse 2
programme.desc: Zoey och gänget undersöker en gammal legend om en PCA-elev som blev galen efter att ha pluggat för mycket inför ett svårt prov. Efter att de råkat störa studentens grav börjar han hemsöka skolan.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Brottningsmästerskapet
programme.desc: Zoey går med i skolans brottningslag, men tränaren låter henne aldrig visa vad hon går för. Vid regionsmästerskapen får hon äntligen chansen att brottas - i mästerskapsmatchen mot en riktigt tuff äldre pojke.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Zoeys ballong
programme.desc: Zoey och gänget får i uppgift att skriva ner sina mest pinsamma hemligheter på papperslappar, som de sedan knyter fast i ballonger. Skoluppgiften får dock en mörk ton när någon får reda på Zoeys hemlighet och börjar utpressa henne.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Chases Farmor
programme.desc: Zoey kommer på den perfekta födelsedagspresenten till Chase när hon får veta att hans älskade farmor fyller år på samma dag som honom. Dustin fastnar med armen i en godisautomat, och Lola och Quinn försöker få loss honom.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Michael hjärta Lisa
programme.desc: Michael har blivit förtjust i Zoeys vän Lisa, men det visar sig att hans känslor sätter käppar i hjulet för honom när han försöker vinna en talangtävling. Logan utmanar samtidigt Chase på en go-kartstävling.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Radion
programme.desc: Chase ärver en gammal radio, som han säljer till Zoey för fem dollar och taco-kupong. Zoey upptäcker dock att radion är värd betydligt mer än vad hon någonsin kunnat ana.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Tjänster och gentjänster
programme.desc: Zoeys favoritförfattare kommer till stan. Hennes försök att hitta en skjuts till eventet leder dock till att hon hamnar i en katastrofal spiral av tjänster och gentjänster.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Massor med revben
programme.desc: När Zoey får ärva en hel lastbil fylld med revben av sin gammelfarbror så bestämmer hon sig för att anordna en grilltävling.

programme.title: Zoey 101: En dräpig historia
programme.desc: Dustin blir uppskrämd efter att ha sett på en skräckfilm och försöker att ta sig ifrån skolan. Samtidigt undersöker killarna vad det är som sätter igång brandlarmet i deras hus varje natt.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Snillen emellan
programme.desc: När ett ungt vetenskapsgeni funderar på att börja på PCA blir Quinn genast upprörd, då hon inser att hon inte längre skulle vara skolans smartaste tjej. Samtidigt tror Michael att han håller på att bli galen.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Son till en dekan
programme.desc: Zoey börjar träffa dekanens son, men finner sig snart mitt i en lottdragningsskandal. Under tiden blir Chase och Michael stämda, då en av deras tecknade filmer anmälts för upphovsrättsbrott.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Händerna på bussen
programme.desc: Gänget är med i en tävling som Blix anordnat, där de måste hålla händerna på en buss så länge som möjligt. Samtidigt uppfinner Quinn en ny munsprej som orsakar ofrivilliga skrattattacker.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Danstävlingen
programme.desc: Den allt annat än väldansande Chase anmäler sig till en danstävling tillsammans med Zoey, efter att hans första danspartner brutit benet. Samtidigt ber Lola om skådespelartips av en kille för att kunna flirta med honom.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Fröken PCA
programme.desc: Lola och Zoey ställer upp i en skönhetstävling på skolan, men det dröjer inte länge förrän tävlingen börjar tära på deras vänskap. Samtidigt försöker Michael övertyga Quinn om att han är rolig.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Barskrapad
programme.desc: Logan måste försöka vänja sig vid ett helt annan liv än vad han är van vid, när hans rike pappa plötsligt bestämmer sig för att inte ge honom mer pengar. Samtidigt påstår sig Michael vara en utbrytarkung.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Farväl, Zoey? del 1
programme.desc: Zoey måste bestämma sig för om hon ska stanna på skolan eller flytta till London med sina föräldrar. Hon ber sina vänner om hjälp, men väntar till allra sist med att berätta nyheten för Chase, vilket inte gör honom glad.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Farväl Zoey? del 2
programme.desc: Zoey måste bestämma sig för om hon ska stanna på skolan eller flytta till London med sina föräldrar. Hon ber sina vänner om hjälp, men väntar till allra sist med att berätta nyheten för Chase, vilket inte gör honom glad.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Glimtar från förr
programme.desc: Nyfikna elever får höra om livet på skolan.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ombytta roller
programme.desc: Michael och Logan försöker lura Miss Burvitch att Chase fortfarande bor kvar i deras rum, så att de ska slippa få en ny rumskamrat. Samtidigt råkar Zoey göra så att Coco får sparken.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Den falska rumskompisen
programme.desc: Efter en inställd resa får gänget spendera påsklovet på skolan alldeles själva. Till en början har de det kul, men det roliga får ett plötsligt stopp när dekanen beskyller pojkarna för vandalisering.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ensamma på PCA
programme.desc: Michael och Logans nya rumskamrat visar sig vara en snygg kille.Det börjar snart spridas ett rykte om att han och Zoey börjat dejta varandra, och nu måste de tillsammans försöka reda ut vem som startat ryktet.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Kärleksryktet
programme.desc: Efter att Logan skickat ett ursinnigt röstmeddelande till Dustin tvingas han gå på en kurs i aggressionshantering. Han försöker att slippa gå dit genom att hålla sig lugn och snäll, men Zoey har andra planer.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Ohanterad ilska
programme.desc: Quinn och Mark bestämmer sig för att ta en paus, men Quinn blir upprörd när hon får syn på Mark med en annan tjej. Oväntat nog finner hon tröst hos Logan, och det hela slutar med en kyss.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Quinn förlorar mark
programme.desc: Zoey återvänder till PCA för att prata med Chase, men inser snart att han åkt till England för att kunna vara med henne. Det visar sig dessutom att Chase måste stanna i London i en hel termin.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Långt gånget.
programme.desc: Zoey hjälper Lola att få ihop de pengar hon lovat att skänka till välgörenhet. Under tiden kommer Quinn och Logan varandra närmare, samtidigt som de försöker hålla sitt förhållande hemligt.

programme.title: Zoey 101: Vince är tillbaka
programme.desc: Gänget blir överraskade när mobbaren Vince Blake plötsligt dyker upp på PCA igen. Tjejerna bestämmer sig för att ignorera honom, medan killarna tycker att det är hög tid för hämnd.

programme.desc: Continuing on from the previous episode’s look at the current Raimon team, this time we take a look at the history of Raimon’s football club, as told by Coach Evans.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Let’s play soccer!
programme.desc: Mark Evans is the captain of the Raimon Middle School’s long-neglected soccer club. With the club on the verge of being disbanded Mark is hoping to kick it into shape, but he’ll need a little help and more than a little luck.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Royal is here!
programme.desc: Raimon have gotten their first piece of good news, they’re going to play an exhibition game! Except that the game is against the toughest team in the whole country.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the killer shot!
programme.desc: The team are still on a high from their surprise win against Royal Academy, but there’s a lot of work they still need to do. Kevin is mad at himself and jealous of Axel for scoring the winning shot.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Here comes the Dragon!
programme.desc: It’s game day for Raimon and they’re playing a team that everyone’s nervous about - Occult Jr High.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Where's the notebook?
programme.desc: The Soccer Frontier Tournament is about to start and Raimon are up against the terrifying jumpers of Wild Junior High in their first game. Everyone agrees that unless they come up with a new move, Raimon are finished before they even start.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is the Inazuma Drop!
programme.desc: Raimon are all pumped up and ready for their big game against Wild Junior High, all except one player - Jack Wallside. His fear of heights is getting in the way of the Inazuma Drop, and without it all is lost.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Showdown at the riverbank!
programme.desc: Raimon are training hard for the next game in the Soccer Frontier Tournament, and people are beginning to sit up and take notice; including their next opponents - Brainwashing Jr High.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The terrifying soccer cyborgs!
programme.desc: It’s another big game for Raimon, against the robots of Brainwashing Jr High. Nobody’s ever scored a goal against them, much less won, but if Raimon want to advance they have to do just that.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Willy rising!
programme.desc: Axel Blaze is injured and out of Raimon’s next game, but their opponents are the weakest team in the whole tournament, so winning shouldn’t be a problem.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The spy from Royal
programme.desc: Raimon Jr Soccer Club is looking stronger than ever, but so are the forces in league against them.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Find a new coach
programme.desc: The big game against Royal is only a few days away, but unless Raimon Jr can find a new coach then they’re going out without even setting foot on the field!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The finals - Royal Academy - first half!
programme.desc: The boys arrive at Royal Academy for the biggest game of their lives, but before they can begin they have to dispel the cloud of suspicion hanging over the place.
programme.sub-title: The finals - Royal Academy - first half!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The finals - Royal Academy - second half!
programme.desc: With Ray Dark safely shut away, the game against Royal has properly begin, and it’s a real game this time not a walkover. It’s neck and neck and back and forth and the air is full of penguins.
programme.sub-title: The finals - Royal Academy - second half!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: The Legendary 11!
programme.desc: The boys still can't believe they beat Royal and are the new District Champion. After the celebratory dust settles, a mysterious figure walks into Seymour’s noodle bar.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: This is it - the National tournament!
programme.desc: The Raimon 11 have set their sights on the National tournament and they’re determined to win it all.
programme.sub-title: This is it - the National tournament!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Soccer - ninja style!
programme.desc: With Nathan still on the team, for now, the Raimon 11 can move forward and concentrate on the Nationals.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven: Jude's decision!
programme.desc: The narrow victory over Shuriken has given Raimon confidence, but on the other side of the tournament there’s shock and awe at Royal’s complete destruction at the hands of Zeus Jr.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Diagnosis: Deletion
programme.desc: Blue Angel’s looking to Speed Duel her way to victory, but the diabolical doctor she’s battling is set on prescribing a dose of defeat!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: The Brave Battler
programme.desc: With LINK VRAINS under attack, it’s up to the flashiest duelist ever to save the day – Shima!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Bugging Out
programme.desc: The fate of LINK VRAINS hangs in the balance as Playmaker faces off against one of Hanoi’s top lieutenants!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Kolter’s Khronicles
programme.desc: The Hanoi have expanded their reach beyond the boundaries of LINK VRAINS, and Kolter’s chronicling the chaos!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! VRAINS: Under VRAINS
programme.desc: Ghost Gal ventures into the vast underbelly of LINK VRAINS and uncovers a sinister secret the Hanoi have been hiding!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Raimon's Football Club Is Rising From The Ashes!?
programme.desc: Determined to destroy Raimon, the Almighty Faith's School players will even risk crippling their opponents. The sight of this triggers an emotional change in Victor.
programme.sub-title: Raimon's Football Club Is Rising From The Ashes!?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: J.P.'s Special Move!
programme.desc: The Raimon Eleven, all finally working together as a real team, defeat Almighty Faith School! But Fifth Sector strikes back, using Victor's sick brother to stop his rebellion and blackmail him into obeying once again.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: A Reunion with Jude Sharp!
programme.desc: As Raimon prepares for its scheduled regional semifinal match with Ivy Selective College, they receive startling news: Raimon has been moved to another bracket in the tournament!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Frozen in Time
programme.desc: When an unexpected phenomenon stops time, Kite is able to gain the upper hand by tapping into Astral's memories and witnessing firsthand the battles that he and Yuma have fought together.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Let the Duels Begin
programme.desc: With the World Duel Carnival about to begin, Yuma gets set to take on the best duelists from around the world… that is, until he realizes he never entered. Can Yuma figure out a way to join the Carnival, or will Yuma’s efforts fall short?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: A Team Performance
programme.desc: The World Duel Carnival kicks off when Yuma is challenged by Striker, a soccer player turned duelist who has one goal in mind: victory.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Heavy Metal
programme.desc: Yuma rises up to the challenge of a pint-sized duelist and his deck of monster machines.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: Love Hurts
programme.desc: Yuma broke Anna’s heart years ago, and now she’s back for revenge. If Yuma loses, he has to be Anna’s boyfriend forever.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ZEXAL: No Tomato
programme.desc: Yuma faces his toughest test to date when he challenges the tomato loving Tombo to a duel. Can Yuma overcome his hate for tomatoes and be victorious, or will his taste buds only be serving up defeat?

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Dreaded Royal Academy!
programme.desc: The match begins, and Sam just barely manages to block a shot on goal -- Royal Academy is proving to be unlike any other team Raimon has faced.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Explosion Ultimate Thunder!
programme.desc: Raimon attempts a comeback using their super tactic, but end up surrendering a goal to Royal Academy instead. Raimon's offense is powerless in the face of Royal Academy's overwhelming special moves.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: A Revolutionary Wind!
programme.desc: The day after their blistering battle in the regional semifinals, the Raimon players are ordered to meet at Royal Academy. There, they learn the stunning truth behind their match with the academy.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 1
programme.desc: Sylvio finally has just the thing to take Yuya down – a deck full of Pendulum Cards! Could Yuya's days in the spotlight be done for?
programme.sub-title: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 1

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 2
programme.desc: Yuya is off his game and on the run as Sylvio zeroes in on zeroing out his life points! If Yuya can’t get into the swing of things, this could be his final performance!
programme.sub-title: The Pendulum Swings Both Ways: Part 2

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Making the Cut: Part 1
programme.desc: Sora is psyched to put on a showstopping duel for the fans, but his opponent Shay is set to turn Sora’s one man show into a no man show!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Making the Cut: Part 2
programme.desc: Sora and Shay's heated duel hits its boiling point when dark secrets about their hidden history come to light! Could there be something sinister behind Sora’s sweet-toothed smile?

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Sora’s Secrets: Part 1
programme.desc: While Yuto is looking for answers, Sora is looking to get some revenge! But when these two tangle, Yuya finds out more than he ever expected!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! ARC-V: Sora’s Secrets: Part 2
programme.desc: Surprises are in the cards as the battle between Sora and Yuto comes to an unexpected conclusion! But just when Yuya thinks he’s seen everything, a new face shows up on the scene that makes Yuya do a triple take!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Ravaging Fangs of the Sea Kings!
programme.desc: Determined to free Football from the clutches of Fifth Sector, the Raimon Eleven prepare to revolt. With the regional championship against Pirates Cove Merchant Marine Academy Academy coming up, morale is high, and losing is not an option.
programme.sub-title: Ravaging Fangs of the Sea Kings!

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: Fly Arion’s Fighting Spirit
programme.desc: The true revolution won't occur until the crowds watching are reminded of the power of real Football and decide to take a stand. The Raimon Eleven welcome back members who had quit, and the regional championship match begins.

programme.title: Inazuma Eleven Go: The Autumn Sky Challengers!
programme.desc: The Holy Road tournament is finally underway. Surrounded by powerful enemies sent by Fifth Sector, the matches ahead will be the toughest yet. So the team practices harder than ever, reminding themselves that no opponent is unbeatable.

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: The Beginning of the End
programme.desc: The grand finale of the World Racing Grand Prix is set to start, and our two finalists -Team 5D's and Team New World - are ready to take center stage. For Yusei, Jack and Crow, second place isn't an option!

programme.title: Yu-Gi-Oh! 5D's: Dawn of the Machines
programme.desc: It's one down and two to go for Team 5D's as Jack and his mighty Red Nova Dragon get set to take on and take out Primo and Jakob of Team New World!

programme.desc: Värmland: Fem unga mystiskt döda - varnar för dödsdrog. Stockholm: After Work-tjuvar fångade på bild. Kristianstad: Tjuvar länsade butik. Nynäshamn: Misshandel vid butiksrån.

programme.title: Efterlyst: Avsnitt 6107
programme.desc: Nynäshamn: Grovt rån mot butik. Luleå: Död person hittad efter brand - Polisen söker skoter. Borås: Vem är mannen som hittades död vid Tränningstorpasjön? Göteborg/Jönköping: Man gripen för mordet på Joullnar.

programme.title: Efterlyst: Avsnitt 6108
programme.desc: Eskilstuna: Polisen söker vittnen till mordförsök. Stockholm: Går till attack inne på McDonalds. Norrköping: Fritagningen vid Vrinnevisjukhuset. Stockholm: Våldsamt rån mot antikhandel.

programme.title: Efterlyst: Avsnitt 6109
programme.desc: Nacka: Grovt rån mot barnfamilj. Varberg: Avbröt misshandel – nomineras till pris. Norrköping: Fritagningen vid Vrinnevisjukhuset. Örebro: Polisen söker deltagare i påskupploppen. Malmö: Kände till mordplan – döms.

programme.title: Efterlyst: Avsnitt 6201
programme.desc: Våldtäktsoffer spelade in det grova övergreppet, polisen vädjar om hjälp att identifiera gärningsmannen. 24-åring döms till fängelse, efter att ha mördat en man för hans jacka och dödshotat Hasse Aro.

programme.title: Efterlyst: Avsnitt 6202
programme.desc: I Efterlyst berättar vi inte bara om brotten, vi löser dem. Programmet sänds live från Stockholm med poliser och experter i studion och på plats där brotten händer, runt om i Sverige.

programme.title: Efterlyst: Avsnitt 6203
programme.desc: En privatperson beskuts av en guldrånare, ungdomar på Snapchat bryter mot barnporrlagen, och två häktas efter Efterlysts inslag om åldringsbrott.

programme.desc: Vågen av gängmord - polisens Hanna Paradis gästar Efterlyst. Karlstad: Fräck klockstöld för 114 000 kronor. Huddinge: 93-årig kvinna bedragen på kort och smycken. Sundsvall: Mordförsöket i Bosvedjan.

programme.desc: Stockholm: Tre män skjutna i Fittja. Norrköping: Tungt gängkriminell fritogs. Örebro: Barn och unga mitt i skottlossning. Stockholm: Bomben I Kungsträdgården.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 11
programme.desc: Sister Benita Wainwright is leading the team, a day that she describes as “Chaos. There are people everywhere. It’s hard going. But staff pull together and make sure patients are looked after.”

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 12
programme.desc: At Barnsley Casualty the team clock on to a backlog of patients waiting to be transferred to wards. With no beds across the entire hospital, Sister Jane Hawksworth is battling to prevent patients being on trolleys for the NHS maximum of 12 hours.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 13
programme.desc: After an extraordinarily busy few days, the team at Barnsley Casualty are struggling to clear the backlog of patients, and new arrivals are waiting up to 5 hours to see a doctor.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 14
programme.desc: Sister Jane Hawksworth is on duty, ‘I think the sister team is strong, we are all strong women.' Sister Benita Wainwright heads to Resus where paramedics rush in a 14-year-old girl having a prolonged epileptic seizure.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 15
programme.desc: It’s been a busy night at Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty Department, so the corridors are already packed full of patients when Sister Benita Wainwright arrives to head the shift.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 16
programme.desc: In charge today at Barnsley Hospital’s Casualty Department is Consultant Doctor Julian Humphrey, ‘Emergency departments may look very chaotic but there’s a reasonable amount of structure. It’s organized chaos!’

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 17
programme.desc: Barnsley Casualty is facing one of its toughest shifts to date. With no children’s beds available across the whole of Yorkshire and a department filling up with poorly children the hospital is under pressure.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 18
programme.desc: Registrar Doctor Gemma Hartshorne prepares to treat a man who has suddenly lost all feeling in his foot. Loss of blood flow is turning Roger's foot white - urgent treatment is needed to prevent amputation.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 19
programme.desc: Trainee Advanced Nurse Practitioner Chantelle Proctor assesses a 49-year-old man rushed in by ambulance. Philip, who has a heart condition, collapsed at home and has been vomiting for the last ten days.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 20
programme.desc: While people enjoy a most wonderful time of the year, Barnsley Hospital Casualty is open for business as usual, and the team are getting into the Christmas spirit. Consultant Doctor Julian Humphrey is leading the festive shift.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 1
programme.desc: While Sister Jane runs outside to help a critical patient in the car park, Matron Val and Consultant Doctor Dave Walker need to negotiate with the Police who are stopping new arrivals entering the building.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 2
programme.desc: Junior Doctor Tom Fish’s first patient is 18-year-old Lewis who has broken bones and deep wounds from a moped accident - but causing him the most pain is his fear of needles.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 3
programme.desc: Sister Benita is running the shift, when suddenly, a fire alarm goes off and she must prepare the entire department - staff and emergency patients - for a full evacuation.

programme.title: Casualty 24/7: Episode 4
programme.desc: Sister Harriet spots Terry waiting in the queue and decides he needs urgent care. He’s fallen off a roof and is unable to move his arm from a position above his head.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 1
programme.desc: Hoarding is on the rise and it's believed that 1 in 20 people could have a problem. With over 1.2 million problem hoarders in the UK today, one could be your neighbour?

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 2
programme.desc: Susan's hoard has made her virtually homeless. Brian has dedicated his life to hoarding and his daughter is sick of it. Jake is lucky to be alive as his home almost burned to the ground in an inferno fuelled by the clutter he'd collected.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 3
programme.desc: Arthur's flat is packed with junk. Experts Caz and Tee are up for their toughest assignment ever. Khim is getting married but first she must clear her hoard. Mandi's passion for vintage clothes is out of control.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 4
programme.desc: Esther's hoard is so bad her landlord told her to clear up or clear out. Nigel receives a visit from fellow hoarder Janice.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 12
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Alan, a sound therapist who has lived on his own for 20 years. His son has tried to help him clean, but it’s a battle he’s never been able to win.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 1
programme.desc: In this brand-new series of Dirty Home Rescue, Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Toni from Telford whose house is so dirty her partner of 10 years, Rich, won’t move in with her.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 2
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Bill and Antionette from Newport, who share their home with their 3 cats. They admit they’ve not deep cleaned their home since they moved in.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 5
programme.desc: Paul's hoard fills his whole house, room after room after room is buried under 6 feet of clutter.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 1
programme.desc: In the picturesque city of Bath, Paul’s cottage is bursting at the seams with a lifetime’s collection of junk. Known locally as ‘boot cottage’ - because everything Paul owns and wears comes from car boot sales - every room is a no-go zone.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 2
programme.desc: In Harlow, 63-year-old Bubbles’ high-rise flat is packed with piles of junk she can’t bear to throw away. But it doesn’t end there she also has a staggering 4 lock ups stuffed to the gills with rubbish.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 3
programme.desc: In Mansfield Sue’s hoard is driving her family and grandchildren away and her husband Neil to distraction. Every room is crammed with clutter including a bedroom that looks more like a dolls graveyard than somewhere to sleep.

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 4
programme.desc: In Liverpool, the Bells are a family at war over hoarding. Mum Betty and son Richard are happy to live in their mess, but son in law Keith is determined that things must change. Can they change the habit of a lifetime and part with their possessions?

programme.title: Hoarders: Episode 5
programme.desc: In the London suburb of Enfield, former workaholic Sandra has become a hoard-aholic since retiring. Her compulsion to spend is out of control, and everything is added to the growing mountains of books, clothes and candles…

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 3
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of married couple Lynne and Keith from Chudleigh in South Devon whose house hasn’t had a deep clean since they moved in nearly 20 years ago.

programme.title: Dirty Home Rescue: Episode 4
programme.desc: Hayley Leitch and her cleaning team Tom Swire and Chesley Medley-Brown go to the rescue of Anita from Manchester, who’s house is overrun with her 3 cats who make a mess wherever they like.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Charlotte, Elvis and Jack
programme.desc: Actress Eileen Davidson's Wheaten terrier puppy Charlotte, plays too rough with her son. Two other dogs react to household triggers, the garbage disposal and shiny floors.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Cesar and the Horse Whisperer (Chloe & Hobo, Ali)
programme.desc: Cesar enlists the help of Horse Whisperer Pat Parelli at a riding center that works with special needs people. A dog with separation anxiety exhibits extreme dog aggression.
programme.sub-title: Cesar and the Horse Whisperer (Chloe & Hobo, Ali)

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Inside Puppy Mills
programme.desc: This powerful episode delves into the horror of puppy mills and the rescue and rehab of traumatized pups by the Last Chance for Animals non-profit organization.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Nuna & Kane
programme.desc: NuNu the Chihuahua, fiercely attacks anyone who comes near his owner Tina. NuNu’s total opposite, Kane the Great Dane, is vehemently afraid of shiny surfaces

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Opie & Flirt
programme.desc: Black lab mix Opie is a charmer around people, but frighteningly aggressive around other dogs. Energetic to the point of being neurotic, Chinese Crested Flirt cannot sit still for one moment.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Rana & Ruby
programme.desc: Scared of everything, Ruby the Vischla deals with her neuroses by biting. At the same time, Rana barks every time bread pops in the toaster, or when the microwave goes off, or when the phone rings.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Josh & Boomer
programme.desc: Josh, a Maltese, will not let anyone with a brush or pair of scissors near him without putting up a fight. Boomer, a Chesapeake Bay Retriever, barks incessantly and refuses to come out of the pool.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Harry & Brooks
programme.desc: Harry wants to charge after anything with wheels, including passing cyclists, rollerbladers or skateboarders. Brooks, an Entlebucher, is constantly chasing after light, he is never calm.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Coach & Sueki
programme.desc: Coach, an out of control Boxer, bit a neighbor, seemingly sealing his fate. Coach gets a stay of execution when Cesar Millan comes to the rescue. Sueki refuses to walk on the leash.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Slick & Pepper
programme.desc: Slick, a rare white Puli, is full of phobias. When clients come to Christopher’s photography studio, they are greeted by Pepper’s annoying barking and heel nipping.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Ava & Gus
programme.desc: Ava, a Pug/Pekingese swiftly twirls for all occasions, possibly a neurological condition Cesar cannot treat. Gus the Bouvier greets people by throwing his 100 pound body at them.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Maya & Churchill
programme.desc: Churchill the Rottweiler is a well mannered dog, except when around other animals. Meanwhile, Maya, an affable Pit Bull, insists on being intimately involved in all operations of the household.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Bubba & Garrett
programme.desc: Heidi Wasserman inherited Bubba, a spoiled Maltese that demands to be taken everywhere and nips at anyone who tries to leave. Garrett, a German Shepherd, chases his tail, obsessively.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Emily
programme.desc: Emily, a Pit Bull, has become every owner’s worst nightmare – extremely aggressive towards other dogs. She’s so out of control, only Cesar Millan’s 6-week boot camp can turn her behavior around.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Hank & Paris
programme.desc: Marsha Alexander’s rescued Mastiff has ruined the furniture and intimidates anyone walking by his gate. Paris, a long hair Chihuahua, looks fashionable, but barks and snaps at strangers.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Sasha & Shep
programme.desc: Lhasa Apso Sasha, bares her teeth at anyone who takes anything from her. White German Shepherd, “Shep,” goes after strangers, making it impossible for his wheelchair bound owner to control.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Jake & King
programme.desc: Jake tends to mind his owner Bob but goes crazy to protect Bob’s wife Linda. At the same time, all of 10 year old Chantel’s might is hardly enough for 150 pound King to even take notice.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Scrawny & Lola
programme.desc: Scrawny, one of nine Yorkies, is Allen’s favorite, but attacks anyone that comes near. Lola, a Dalmatian, barks at everything. Find out how Cesar reestablishes control in both homes.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: J & Alice
programme.desc: J is unpredictable and aggressive and his owner is now dealing with a lawsuit. Alice is depressed and aggressive towards the other two dogs in the house – a potentially lethal combination.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Caper & Julius
programme.desc: Caper has a lot of energy, particularly when it comes to chasing down balls non-stop. Julius is a four-year-old Pit Bull mix that is frightened of everything.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Bella & Jordan
programme.desc: “Bella Angel” is a devil in disguise. She bites anyone who comes near the house or the family. Jordan, an English Bulldog, jumps up and down, licks people incessantly and is obsessed by skateboards.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Sunshine & Teddy
programme.desc: Sunshine is a champion Doberman in the show ring but far too aggressive in the street. Teddy, a yellow lab, has bitten its owner twice, and has attacked more than one stranger.

programme.title: Mannen som talar med hundar: Goldie & Pepsi
programme.desc: Pepsi, a German Shepherd, becomes intensely aggressive around cats. Goldie, the beautiful Brittany Spaniel of “General Hospital” star Jacklyn Zeman that has become aggressive towards female dogs.
